{"tid":2493751,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"十八歲生日","createTime":"2021-04-18T06:54:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T07:33:59.000Z","uid":394095,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"35134be6d344896c806c181b4e071b21eacdde91","tid":2493751,"uid":394095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T06:54:27.000Z","msg":"話說小弟早前移民咗去外國，雖則英文ok,但係個度人生路不熟。離開香港一段時間之後同香港啲朋友嘅關係又疏淡如水。今日小弟十八歲生日，無朋友又去唔到邊度，想毒毒地乞句生日快樂。<br />\n<br />\n人到外國唔知係咪疫情關係，成日都有啲攰，不過有無乜點後悔。sor for 1999<br />\n<br />\n<strong>生日願望：光復香港，時代革命</strong><br />\n<strong>香港獨立，唯一出路</strong><br />\n<strong>祝願中蝈早日支爆</strong>"},{"pid":"20881fe1cacd1214aef81b9dded468ce00d94bf1","tid":2493751,"uid":252541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T06:55:23.000Z","msg":"生日快樂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e7b87bc19705177acc9b5a4c8bb499bad373f81","tid":2493751,"uid":307927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T06:55:38.000Z","msg":"生日快樂<br />\n但國安法下 我只能祝願祖國日益強大<br />\n他朝你學有所成便回國建設"},{"pid":"5e4f3bd660c23d6e7f6a25eecb52389aa5b74e6a","tid":2493751,"uid":181160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T06:57:26.000Z","msg":"生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705a579cdc8dfb0bbbe95f8cfd1578bb28bab239","tid":2493751,"uid":308558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T06:59:34.000Z","msg":"生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e1d296a376b720814af82d4abd6af79e78c70af","tid":2493751,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T07:16:59.000Z","msg":"破處未？<br />\nHappy birthday"},{"pid":"7b0bf44b46bf87aeb0f5a4432f68264